<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- While they can be combined with the membership form (DRY), I might change up how the admin status is given so I won't prematurely optimize my code here -->
  <section class="admin-form-section">
    <form action="/membership/admin" method="POST" novalidate>
      <h1>Become an Admin</h1>
      <p>Have the ability to delete users however you wish! But first, you must answer the one true ring... uh I meant riddle.</p>
      <section>
        <!-- It's Moderator! -->
        <p>
          <label for="answer">I hold the gate where riddles spin. Order I keep, chaos I pin; who am I?</label>
          <input type="text" id="answer" name="answer" maxlength="25" value="<%= locals.previousValues?.answer %>" required>
          <span class="error" role="alert" aria-live="polite">
            <%= locals.errors?.find(error => error.path === 'answer')?.msg %>
          </span>
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <button type="submit">Answer</button>
      </section>
    </form>
  </section>
</body>
</html>